# Documentation

The game is hosted by a server that provides a gRPC services called `GameService`.

The service has two methods that can be called: `Start` and `Act`.

## Starting a game

There are two types of games that can be started: a training session or a quest.


### Training

Finishes once this level is completed. Can be run in parallel with other users. As oftern as you want.


### Quest

Only one user at a time is allowed to play a quest. If you start a quest while another user is already playing, you will be queued. Shown on dashboard.




